{
  "stem": "27335.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after my-- my exposure on Budapest-- Budapest television, all these people came, telephoned, and letters, and the messages and so-- to the station, to the party office, to the whole Federation of Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to see that-- speak to this guy-- mostly-- mostly Jewish people, and the cousins of-- cousins of Hannah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is Sass, his name-- S-- S-A-S-S.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sass [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I looked him up, because he called and so on, and selected a day and went to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was-- he went-- he visited Israel once or twice-- twice a year, and wrote a certain time-- wrote a long, long letter to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Szenes again, and so on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he handed the letter over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow-- somehow they weren't sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when I had the television interview in Budapest, the Tel Aviv radio denounced me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who this man coming 20 or 25 or 30 years later, coming in from Canada into Hungary, and proclaims himself, and reveals himself and claims that Hannah Szenes was his fiance?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's an imposter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's a crook.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they used a name-- in Israel, a Hungarian national used his name that he was in Budapest at the time when I was on the television.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that man-- and I think found out from [INAUDIBLE]-- that man protested the radio, on radio, to distract this because he never heard my name.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He never knew-- heard anything ever about me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Why they use his name, this [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This man.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This Israeli man--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he simply-- simply said, because they-- they used his name on the radio, when they denounced me, that this so and so person--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was in Budapest when this Canadian-- Canadian Andrew Durovecz was on television and claimed Hannah Szenes to himself.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
